吉布森（Gibson）宣布杰夫·贝克（Jeff Beck）'Yardburst'1959 Les Paul标准定制吉他https://www.nme.com/news/music/gibson-annouse-jeff-beck-yardburst-1959-les-paul-paul-paul-standard-custom-gutar-3768477？ Beck-Yardburst 1959-LES-PAUL-CUSTOM-GUTARLiberty Dunworth Tue, 25 Jun 2024 11:51:04 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3768477 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杰夫·贝克（Jeff Beck）与1959年的莱斯·保罗（Les Paul）标准" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>吉他到了他的80岁生日，只制作了130个型号</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gibson-announce-jeff-beck-yardburst-1959-les-paul-standard-custom-guitar-3768477">吉布森（Gibson）邮报宣布，杰夫·贝克（Jeff Beck）&#39;Yardburst&#39;1959年Les Paul Standard Custom Guitar</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杰夫·贝克（Jeff Beck）与1959年的莱斯·保罗（Les Paul）标准" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>吉布森（Gibson）分享了1959年新的“ Yardburst”的细节，以纪念吉他偶像<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeff-beck">杰夫·贝克（Jeff Beck）</a>制作的Les Paul Custom。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/music-greats-deaths-in-2023-3558913">记住我们在2023年失去的音乐巨人</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>吉他制造商庆祝130张音乐历史，以及在传奇人物庆祝他的80岁生日的同一天，新车型既到来了）。</p><p>它向贝克（Beck）首次放在地图上时扮演的斧头向斧头表示敬意 - 他在作为Yardbirds的一部分中取名的标志性1959 Les Paul Standard。 “ Yardburst”现在可用，是对历史吉他的忠实娱乐性，旨在捕捉其所有独特的特征，包括经典的白色梭芯Humbuckers和Black Black Single-Ply Pickguard。</p><p>只有130个与吉布森（Gibson）130周年保持一致，每个人都是在墨菲（Murphy）实验室手工制作的，并巧妙地老化以匹配吉他手时代原始模型的确切外观。</p><p>这是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-guitarist-jeff-beck-has-died-aged-78-3379009">在去年一月的78岁那年1月的吉他先驱者意外死亡</a>之后。 </p><figure id="attachment_3768480" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3768480" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3768480" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson-Body@2000x1270.jpg" alt="杰夫·贝克·吉布森（Jeff Beck Gibson）&#39;Yardburst&#39;" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson-Body@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson-Body@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson-Body@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson-Body@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson-Body@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson-Body@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3768480" class="wp-caption-text">杰夫·贝克·吉布森（Jeff Beck Gibson）&#39;Yardburst&#39;。学分：吉布森</figcaption></figure><p>他的遗ow桑德拉·贝克（Sandra Beck）说：“杰夫（Jeff）为拥有这把吉他的原始作品感到非常自豪。” “他意识到并完全支持 Gibson Custom 为创造这把乐器所做的出色工作和热爱，并希望这把吉他能给演奏它的人带来数小时的乐趣。”</p><p>吉布森（Gibson）首席执行官Cesar Gueikian在宣布该模型后也向贝克分享了他的致敬。他说：“杰夫是开拓者，是我们吉他英雄的吉他英雄，并受到同时代人的钦佩。”</p><p> “杰夫在Yardbirds时代的职业生涯的早期吉布森·莱斯·保罗（Gibson Les Paul）的文化意义中发挥了重要作用。就像 Jeff 受到 Les Paul 的影响一样，他也影响了许多标志性音乐家，让他们用 Gibson Les Paul 来创作艺术。我们很荣幸向杰夫致敬。”</p><p>贝克（Beck）于1965年加入Yardbirds，以替代<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eric-clapton">埃里克·克莱普顿（Eric Clapton）</a> 。他与乐队合作了仅12个月以上，并且在阵容的一部分中与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jimmy-page">吉米·佩奇（Jimmy Page）</a>合作短暂合作。</p><p>吉他有黑樱桃的阳光颜色，并带有老化的Lifton Hardshell表壳。现在可以在Gibson上以8,999英镑的价格使用，但似乎已经售罄。 <a href="https://www.gibson.com/en-GB/p/Electric-Guitar/Jeff-Beck-YardBurst-1959-Les-Paul-Standard/Dark-Cherry-Sunburst" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处</a>以获取更多信息。 </p><figure id="attachment_3768479" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3768479" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3768479" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-certificate@2000x1270.jpg" alt="杰夫·贝克·吉布森（Jeff Beck Gibson）&#39;Yardburst&#39;证书" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-certificate@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-certificate@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-certificate@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-certificate@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-certificate@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-certificate@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3768479" class="wp-caption-text">杰夫·贝克·吉布森（Jeff Beck Gibson）&#39;Yardburst&#39;证书。学分：吉布森</figcaption></figure><p>在其他杰夫·贝克（Jeff Beck）的新闻中，今年早些时候，人们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-mark-knopfler-star-studded-going-home-teenage-cancer-trust-3601691">确认了由Mark Knopfler重新录制的版本“ Rot Home”捕获的最后一部录音室唱片。</a></p><p>这首曲目是为了为青少年癌症信托慈善机构筹集资金的重新构想，并以吉他界的一些知名人士为特色，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">皇后</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-may">布莱恩·梅</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">黑安息日</a>的托尼·艾米米（Tony Iommi），埃里克·克拉普顿（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eric-clapton">Eric Clapton）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚动石头</a>吉他手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ronnie-wood">罗尼·伍德（Ronnie Wood）</a>等等。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gibson-announce-jeff-beck-yardburst-1959-les-paul-standard-custom-guitar-3768477">吉布森（Gibson）邮报宣布，杰夫·贝克（Jeff Beck）&#39;Yardburst&#39;1959年Les Paul Standard Custom Guitar</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
